dct_title_s: Okayama-ken shichōson-sei kuiki sangoku zenzu Yamamoto Shinʼichirō.
dct_description_sm: Mounted cover title. Copperplate print. In Japanese. Relief shown by hachures. Includes 1 inset: Okayama shigaizu. Includes list of district names, distance chart, and legend. Engraved by Fujii Kōzaburō. 4 pieces joined 1 map: col.; 96 x 71 cm., folded in cover 17 x 11 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
